Project: fs/lustre-release&lt;br/&gt;
Branch: master&lt;br/&gt;
Current Patch Set: 1&lt;br/&gt;
Commit: c87bdcfab1cdea0e1fe0b2d41f8ea513c65bfc0e&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="238795" author="simmonsja" created="Tue, 18 Dec 2018 20:31:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;pdsh &amp;#45;w mgs_server lctl &amp;#42;.&amp;#42;.$FSNAME&amp;#42;&amp;#45;.active=0&quot;&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
